{"tid":209472,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"招keyboard 作曲/夾band","createTime":"2017-04-20T08:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T02:56:39.000Z","uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed498f9036583449fa8a2d50c707cb491b4dc94","tid":209472,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"我地係本地新手band,form 左一年多啲, 玩開 pop rock, e.g. One ok rock, Supper moment <br />\n黎緊可能參加一啲比賽/出下啲show/busking<br />\n<br />\n不過差嗰keyboard 玩嘅野無咁多變化，啲歌無咁full. 所以我地誠招keyboard一齊撚歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nKeyboard 最好識啲樂理+ 有relative pitch ，技術唔係最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地新浦崗有間band 房，得閒可以上去hea 。不過長夾就可能要夾房租+自備器材. 房租每人每月600-800左右<br />\n<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/wai880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwai880&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=904f6d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wai880</a>"},{"pid":"1e85ce06979d5b1b153c37f5f3fde56110e9df94","tid":209472,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7edffc2777d74295c5f165f22351114722fca308","tid":209472,"uid":93443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"我估係香港夾band真係冇幾多個有relative pitch"},{"pid":"efefe8008022d1c3f3cda34500288c1d1a910926","tid":209472,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我估係香港夾band真係冇幾多個有relative pitch</blockquote><br />\n我識兩個keyboard 有perfect pitch 不過冇時間夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRelative pitch 執多啲歌就有"},{"pid":"a27d79c67b41e71fca5afd1d0672a4c5f2da36e4","tid":209472,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a15d8cc4e458f3cfb7b6f4755f34cc9aaaf2e008","tid":209472,"uid":100700